     C*
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  SET DATA FOR SCREEN
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           @SCRN1    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     RRN1
